Text: I'm confused how you can call that dumb shit super high me, a must see anything?

Well, at least you can always trust the TPB 'community' to be a bunch of leeches and a-holes. How nice of you to seek out and comment on my torrent just to say that you don't like the movie.  

Obviously, the term "must see" is the subjective opinion of the uploader. Did you know? There are whole websites devoted to movie criticism. Perhaps you could share your opinions on movies there, among your fellow d-bag critics. 

GFY.
